title: Things you didn't know about Marine Le Pen
text: Things you didn't know about Marine Le Pen Things you didn't know about Marine Le Pen   Marine Le Pen is a French politician who is the president of the National Front, a national-conservative political party in France and one of its main political forces. Photo: 1 / 10 > POLITIQUE-FRONT NATIONAL-LE PEN Described as more democratic and republican than her nationalist father, she has led a movement of "de-demonization of the Front National" to detoxify it and soften its image [ AFP/Getty Images ] Also in this Gallery
